OL,3,CFarmers in Wales 'losing out' over
OL,4,C'Clarkson's Clause'
OL,6,FThere are calls for an overhaul of
OL,7,Fplanning regulations, to help farmers
OL,8,Fwho want to convert old agricultural
OL,9,Fbuildings .
OL,11,FThis year saw changes in England which
OL,12,Fhas streamlined that process for many,
OL,13,Fbut farmers in Wales say they're
OL,14,Flosing out.
OL,16,FRalph runs a cider stand in the welsh
OL,17,Ffood village at the Royal Welsh Show,
OL,18,Fselling the produce from his farm near
OL,19,FNew Radnor, 5 miles from the English
OL,20,Fborder.
