OL,3,CFarmers in Wales 'losing out' over
OL,4,C'Clarkson's Clause'
OL,6,FShows like this one around Wales are
OL,7,Fthe lifeblood of Ralph's family
OL,8,Fbusiness, which he runs with his son
OL,9,FJames.
OL,11,FThat's because for years they've not
OL,12,Fbeen able to sell their produce from
OL,13,Fthe farm.
OL,15,FAfter mastering the art of cider,
OL,16,FRalph and James are now trying their
OL,17,Fhand at making wine - as a way to
OL,18,Ffurther diversify the farm business.
