OL,3,CFarmers in Wales 'losing out' over
OL,4,C'Clarkson's Clause'
OL,6,F"The vines we planted here they're
OL,7,Fabout three or four years old at the
OL,8,Fmoment, so this is all ready to go,"
OL,9,Fsaid James.
OL,11,FHe wants to convert a building on his
OL,12,Ffarm into a farm-shop- to sell the
OL,13,Fcider and wine he makes from the
OL,14,Fgrapes and apples in his vinyard and
OL,15,Forchard.
OL,17,F"2019 we started out with a plan- it's
OL,18,Fbeen a long drawn out affair to get to
OL,19,Fthis stage at the moment. The planning
OL,20,Fhas been granted now."
