OL,3,CFarmers in Wales 'losing out' over
OL,4,C'Clarkson's Clause'
OL,6,FThe UK Government made reforms to
OL,7,Fwhat's called Permitted Development
OL,8,Fregulations in May.
OL,10,FThese allow for some some agricultural
OL,11,Fbuildings to be converted for other
OL,12,Fuses.
OL,14,FThe issue has recently gained large
OL,15,Fattention, Jeremy Clarkson, himself a
OL,16,Fconvert from petrol head to farmer
OL,17,Ffaced numerous hurdles to develop a
OL,18,Fbarn on his land into a restaurant.
