OL,3,CFarmers in Wales 'losing out' over
OL,4,C'Clarkson's Clause'
OL,6,FBut the changes made to the
OL,7,Fregulations, nicknamed Clarkson's
OL,8,FClause - apply only to England because
OL,9,Fplanning law is devolved.
OL,11,FJames hopes to open the farm shop by
OL,12,FChristmas - after a huge investment of
OL,13,Fmoney, and time.
OL,15,FThe rural advocacy organisation,
OL,16,FCountry, Land and Business Cymru says
OL,17,Fplanning reform in Wales would boost
OL,18,Fthe rural economy.
