OL,3,CFarmers in Wales 'losing out' over
OL,4,C'Clarkson's Clause'
OL,6,FVic Bond is the Director of CLA Cymru,
OL,7,Fshe says "the planning system can't
OL,8,Fkeep up with the demand and with the
OL,9,Fmodern needs of rural communities."
OL,11,F"The time it takes, the cost it takes,
OL,12,Fto get through a planning application,
OL,13,Fwhere these are existing buildings,
OL,14,Fthey're not new, where housing is
OL,15,Fneeded ,for holiday lets, or farm-
OL,16,Fshops."
OL,18,FBack in New Radnor, there's relief to
OL,19,Fbe reaching the end of their planning
OL,20,Fobstacle courseJApple trees have have
OL,21,Fstood here since the 1830s.
